cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.MM

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with human pose estimation in natural images using deep learning techniques.
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes an end-to-end architecture that involves joint training of multiple components.
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with the generation and scoring of pose proposals using a classifier and regressor.
4. cs.RO (Robotics) is a possible category as the paper deals with 3D pose estimation, which is relevant for robotics applications.
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a possible category as the paper deals with processing and analyzing images to extract human pose information.
